Helps users that use the program "Discord" also known as "Discordapp" see any images they have downloaded. This works on Discord's Stable, Canary, and PTB builds. 
It also lets you copy images to your clipboard, save them for viewing later, and clear them within one click. 


/===========\
INSTALL UPDATES VIA THE SOFTWARE MANAGER, NOT THROUGH THE APP ITSELF, A PATCH TO HAVE THE UPDATE BUTTON LAUNCH THE APP WILL COME AT A LATER DATE